Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲大人 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.84,0:00:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子 饿了呢
Comment: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN===================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 早晨刚下的新鲜鸡蛋做的太阳蛋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,做成半熟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.70,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.77,0:02:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您一大早是去市场了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夹这个看起来很好吃的半熟太阳蛋的面包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.35,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,被你发现啦 凯露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我有件事和大家商量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了市场 发现商品很少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,问过情况 似乎是魔物在连接街道的大桥上住下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小麦和其他商品没法流通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那可真是难办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,要是国家… 兰德索尔想想办法就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.94,0:03:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知为什么 王宫不肯行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我去了公会管理协会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也有挂出委托 所以特别想接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看看委托等级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要一大早就拿这么吓人的委托来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露酱 不要这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很头疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:04:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 你要是肯接 我就每天早上抱你叫你起床
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}就算打倒魔物 桥坏了就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}所以 先把它引出来再打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}具体怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}我的护肩能让防御力飞跃性提高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}做诱饵的人请把魔物从桥边引出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1}一般情况下不会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 二货丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这种任务呆子佑树和可萝助怎么可能做得来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我明明是靠头脑吃饭的 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上虽然不情愿 但还是接下诱饵任务的凯露酱最爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跑得这么快 绊倒后确实干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,二货丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:05:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要我陪你胡来 这是最后一次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 凯露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,确实干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2600,3200,\frx720)\blur3\be3}Princess Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 兰德索尔的人们也能吃得饱饱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露酱 佑树君 可可萝酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 不要抱这么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,确认好了 Elder Horn讨伐任务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 请填写这份资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏可萝助耐心教他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这是主人努力的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你努力了呢 佑树君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,美食殿的活动报告居然交给了佑树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很有远见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 这里填错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂的时候不要装懂 尽管问啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,字不能随便写哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伊卡其和查理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们听说啦 您把魔物干掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是大姐{\fnFOT-Humming Std D\fs84}☆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,安子阿姨？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,找你好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.82,0:07:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是佩可酱把魔物干掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我们能进货啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,市场都进不来货 我还以为不行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这样大家就能吃上好吃的了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德索尔就是要充满大家的笑容呢{\fnFOT-Humming Std D\fs84}♪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露大人也被感谢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去吃个午后的小小甜点吧{\fnFOT-Humming Std D\fs84}☆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,小？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是来兰德索尔第一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你们两个有吃过？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是查理告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的可丽饼很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但不知为什么卖的不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.67,0:08:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是个不为人知的好店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 璃乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,会给客人添麻烦的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叫得像杀鸡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不吃金币了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,钱 很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,以前您给的可丽饼 很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的两位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好风景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.02,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来来 毕竟是弟弟君的公会 大优惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,放开了吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 烤面皮要跟不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这边盖顶的水果要用光啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不许说泄气话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们说过要大优惠啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那家店不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好奢侈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要感谢佑树君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,今后请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,成功啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他开心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,弟弟君的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,佑树 佑树 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,梦… 不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么可能忘记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你和很多人增进了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才唤醒了你的深层记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 刚才的既是梦也是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是重复了无数次的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能是未来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时刻接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉一直在催你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我只能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你 佑树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,剑的修行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你终于产生作为剑士的自觉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太用力 感觉剑的重量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.28,0:13:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,主人日复一日的努力 一定会开花结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他像这样 度过了毫不松懈的每一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,佑树君 加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了就没法打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭是一切的根本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,OK…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太可靠了 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说来 凯露酱很慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她说办完事再来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都快吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露酱来了再点一份一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的 你见过尤斯缇雅娜大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德索尔代代都是公主大人当君主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是瞄到一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可是王族怎么说呢 就是有那个气质
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,自然而然就散发出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美得惊为天人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,希望她能对我们这些下人好一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她才不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.52,0:14:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不然这个城镇治安变得这么差 她不可能不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,来兰德索尔这么久了 却没有机会见到公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我这种村里长大的来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是童话人物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什么样的人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,给 要分着吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 我也去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,吃饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正好 我们现在也正要去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.48,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们陪你去 凯露姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.82,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一直在喝酒呢 有好好工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}惊 那那那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,比如那种事 还有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,继续努力 佑树君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不好啦 兰德索尔的城里出现了魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露姐本来和我们在一起 但走丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,王宫骑士团在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要保护这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不要轻言放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,果然已经不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.26,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,王宫骑士团还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,公主呢 尤斯缇雅娜大人在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}安子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.73,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}最后 我要把一直没能说出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs54}登米？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,登米！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对安子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,登米？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,登米！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,登米 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,安子阿姨 你快跑 这里交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 对上这种怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不要勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露酱 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.72,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护大家 请帮我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,全力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1200,1800,\frx720)\blur3\be3}Princess Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真不愧是佩可丽奴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Strike居然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,凯露大人 佩可丽奴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.56,0:18:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 凯露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那个护肩会守护凯露酱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 为什么要自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这种东西 我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.23,screen,,0,0,0,,{\fsp18\fs48\fad(700,0)\bord1\blur15\3c&HEBEBEB&\3a&H14&\fn@simsun\frz270\pos(840,550)}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.24,screen,,0,0,0,,{\fsp18\fs48\fad(700,0)\bord1\blur15\3c&HEBEBEB&\3a&H14&\fn@simsun\frz270\pos(840,550)}为什么你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.25,screen,,0,0,0,,{\fsp18\fs48\fad(700,0)\bord1\blur15\3c&HEBEBEB&\3a&H14&\fn@simsun\frz270\pos(840,550)}要为了别人……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}佩可丽奴！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,弱小的家伙扔下不管不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要理不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.33,0:20:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要守护
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明打算扔下你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这样的 你这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我马上用恢复魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.77,0:21:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.27,0:22:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,主人！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴 凯露
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.64,0:22:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可可萝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我把大家送去安全的地方隔离了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,唷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.24,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可丽饼的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.36,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 我是可丽饼店长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.72,0:23:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,掩人耳目的假身份
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.31,0:23:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,城里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,佩可丽奴大人？
